lastCommitMessage: refactor: clean up code and improve routing logic
- Updated analysis_options.yaml to disable the avoid_print warning.
- Removed unused code and comments in simple_test_runner.dart and test_migrator.dart for better readability.
- Cleaned up order_management_test_refactored.dart by removing an unused function.
- Eliminated unused methods in auth_error_handler.dart and test_auth_isolation.dart to streamline the codebase.
- Adjusted routing logic in admin_route_guard.dart and route_guard.dart to use replacePath instead of replaceNamed for consistency.
- Removed unused constants in public_store_preview_page.dart and user_store_page.dart to enhance maintainability.
These changes improve code clarity and maintainability across the project.
